metadata.name: The hangar oath.
metadata.description:
決戦前夜にいろんな複雑な気持ちを紛らわしながら、苦楽を共にしてきた愛機と語りながら整備して翌日の出撃に備えてる様子を描きました。

「相棒、いよいよ明日だね・・・私の命はお前に預けたよ・・・」

絵を見てくれた人、それぞれのストーリーを感じてもらえたらうれしいです。

I depicted the scene where, on the eve of the battle, he was preparing for the next day's sortie by talking with his beloved aircraft with which he had shared many hardships while confusing his various complicated feelings.

I was talking with my beloved plane, which I had shared many complicated experiences with, and preparing for the next day's battle.

I would be happy if you could feel the story of each person who looked at the picture.
